window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The final book in the epic Alex Hawk Time Travel Adventure saga!</b></p> <p>Alex Hawk has trained the far-flung armies of Kragdon-ah. Now, Alex and his armies will face a fanatical enemy bent on taking over all of Kragdon-ah. Can the armies of Kragdon-ah stand up to the giant Northmen, or will they need help from an unexpected source?</p> <p>Battle for Kragdon-ah <i>is the ninth and final book in the Alex Hawk Time Travel Adventure series. Contains a special note from the author.</i></p>"; 
